<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>미르중식 쿠폰</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: '맑은 고딕', 'Malgun Gothic', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  }
  .mir-wrap {
    max-width: 420px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .mir-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: #E24B4A;
    border: 1.5px solid #E24B4A;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .mir-headline {
    font-size: 34px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #111;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    word-break: keep-all;
  }
  .mir-headline .red { color: #E24B4A; }
  .mir-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .mir-coupon {
    background: #E24B4A;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .mir-coupon::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -30px; right: -30px;
    width: 100px; height: 100px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .mir-coupon::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -40px; left: -20px;
    width: 130px; height: 130px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .mir-coupon-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .mir-coupon-offer {
    font-size: 34px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .mir-coupon-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .mir-divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .mir-divider::before, .mir-divider::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: #eee;
  }
  .mir-divider span { font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; white-space: nowrap; }
  .mir-instruction {
    background: #f8f8f8;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .mir-instruction-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .mir-instruction-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #555;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .mir-brand {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111;
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
  }
  .mir-brand-sub { font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; margin: 0 0 2rem; }
  .mir-stamp {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #aaa;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .mir-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: #4CAF50;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="mir-wrap">
  <div class="mir-tag">미르중식 × 명지대</div>
  <h1 class="mir-headline">맛있는 식사 먹을 기회,<br><span class="red">아직도 미루고 있어?</span></h1>
  <p class="mir-sub">미루지 말고 미르로.<br>이 화면이 당신의 쿠폰입니다.</p>
  <div class="mir-coupon">
    <p class="mir-coupon-label">지금 바로 사용 가능</p>
    <p class="mir-coupon-offer">음료 1잔<br>무료 증정</p>
    <p class="mir-coupon-desc">방문 시 이 화면을 직원에게 보여주세요<br>1인 1회 사용 가능</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mir-divider"><span>사용 방법</span></div>
  <div class="mir-instruction">
    <p class="mir-instruction-title">이렇게 하세요</p>
    <p class="mir-instruction-text">
      1. 미르중식 방문<br>
      2. 주문 후 이 화면 보여주기<br>
      3. 음료 무료로 받기
    </p>
  </div>
  <p class="mir-brand">미르중식</p>
  <p class="mir-brand-sub">명지대학교 정문 앞</p>
  <div class="mir-stamp">
    <div class="mir-dot"></div>
    <span>미르지 말고 미르로</span>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
